      <title>南非主要反对党对联合政府抱有乐观态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/south-african-election-main-opposition-sees-room-for-optimism-on-coalition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非主要反对党民主联盟领导人表示，投资者对该党将与非国大达成联合执政协议组建下一届政府的乐观态度没有错，该党愿意进行以国家利益为优先的谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/south-african-election-main-opposition-sees-room-for-optimism-on-coalition</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 14:54:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国议员对瓦根克内西特提起煽动性投诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/german-lawmaker-files-incitement-complaint-against-wagenknecht</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国一名保守党议员已对极左翼德国社会主义运动党 (BSW) 党员萨拉·瓦根克内西特 (Sahra Wagenknecht) 提起法律诉讼，指控她在上个月的竞选集会上对他发表的言论构成煽动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/german-lawmaker-files-incitement-complaint-against-wagenknecht</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 14:38:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>这些将决定莫迪未来的印度王者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/here-are-the-india-kingmakers-who-will-determine-modi-s-future</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在印度大选中未能获得多数票后，纳伦德拉·莫迪的未来现在掌握在两个出了名的不可靠的盟友手中。]]></description>
