    <item>
      <title>莫迪誓言即使失去印度多数席位仍将继续执政</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/modi-poised-to-lose-india-majority-need-allies-to-keep-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管纳伦德拉·莫迪的政党在议会中失去多数席位，但他仍誓言继续担任印度总理，这迫使他自十年前上台以来首次依靠盟友组建政府。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/modi-poised-to-lose-india-majority-need-allies-to-keep-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 11:54:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国称乌克兰问题计划获支持 峰会受阻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/china-says-its-ukraine-plan-is-winning-support-after-summit-snub</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国最高外交官表示，已有二十多个国家表示支持北京解决俄乌冲突的愿景。几天前，中国表示将不参加即将在瑞士举行的和平峰会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/china-says-its-ukraine-plan-is-winning-support-after-summit-snub</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 11:07:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>缅甸影子政府预示经济动荡加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/myanmar-s-shadow-government-flags-deepening-economic-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[缅甸影子民族团结政府的估计显示，缅甸货币暴跌、美元储备大幅减少以及通货膨胀飙升，正使缅甸经济陷入更深的危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/myanmar-s-shadow-government-flags-deepening-economic-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 09:41:16 GMT</pubDate>
